description: Variation of Condition 1 of the hybrid planning permission reference 2013/3223 (dated 20 August 2014) and subsequently updated by application 2017/5001 dated 01 November 2018 to allow the substitution of drawings for the Phase 2 detailed component of the Woodberry Down Masterplan, namely to facilitate alterations to Block B within Phase 2 comprising amendments to the facades, omission of the car park at podium level, removal of the podium, an increase of 34 units from 241 (consented) to 275 (proposed) and minor layout alterations.
